# Generation 15: the parrot grows up. Input it can't parse is met with an
# honest admission of non-understanding — not echoed (the gen0 parrot is
# retired), and not a wrong "No." (TASKLIST T16).
# (gen52: "how are you?" is now a recognized social act, so it is no longer an
# example of non-understanding — replaced with genuinely unparseable prose.)
